message.content: cs.AR, cs.AR is the most likely category as the paper proposes a hardware-based framework for cache compression. Other likely categories could be cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as the paper discusses techniques to store multiple compressed cache blocks within a physical cacheline, cs.AR (Architecture) as the paper proposes a framework for efficient cache compression, cs.PL (Programming Languages) as the paper discusses the implementation of the Touche framework, cs.SE (Software Engineering) as the paper proposes a new framework for cache compression.
